14 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
15 Sec. 1. 32 V.S.A. § 3754 is amended to read:
16 § 3754. POWERS AND DUTIES OF BOARD
17 (a) The Board shall meet at least annually, prior to February 1, to review all
18 past current use land values for agricultural land and managed forestland
19 recommended by past boards, to review the criteria for lands previously
20 established, and to establish new criteria and values as legislation and land
